Subject: Re: [T2] '69 Single Cab Battery Tray, treasure doors?

Battery Trays are unique to the 68-79 Pickups, but you might get a Splittie
version to fit, I really dunno, I just know the listings from factory VW
listings are different.  Bus Depot is the only US domestic supplier of the
correct Battery Tray I've seen out there, but others may know better.

http://www.busdepot.com/details.jsp?partnumber=261813162M
